  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Last Contingency is an immersive survival game blending intense gunplay, crafting, and farming elements. Created by a passionate two-person team, this low-budget project is a labor of love and a learning experience for us. Currently in pre-release, we're committed to providing regular updates and improvements. We value your feedback—if you find any bugs or have suggestions, please let us know on our Discord. <br><br>Thank you for joining us on this journey!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Last Contingency is an immersive survival game blending intense gunplay, crafting, and farming elements. Created by a passionate two-person team, this low-budget project is a labor of love and a learning experience for us. Currently in pre-release, we're committed to providing regular updates and improvements. We value your feedback—if you find any bugs or have suggestions, please let us know on our Discord. <br><br>Thank you for joining us on this journey!</p>",
